1. Create IAM User and attach AdministratorAccess policy and Dwonload Accesskey and secret key using AWS Console

#Install the AWS CLI for Windows
2. https://awscli.amazonaws.com/AWSCLIV2.msi

#Verify the installation
3. aws --version

#Configure the IAM user on your windows desktop
4. PS C:\WINDOWS\system32> aws configure
